values:
No i havent updated this for ages and ages Holly.  I was trying to get a myspace but i don't know how.

Im so sad today and feel like crying, i might have a wee cry later.  I feel like ive made a horrible mistake coming to manchester and my tutorials are horrible.  I don't know why they let me in, everyone knows so much more than me.  I wish I could articulate my feelings better but i just can't.

i hope this is just a down day.

xx
i also meant i got a  bag in accessorize.oh dear.

i meant to say mr grays says it IS  illgal and the fit things in oasis are,er shoes.i dont mean i just went into the shop and went FFFFIIIIIIIIIITTTTTTTT.Though you probably guessed they were shoes and not door knobs or something.
in other news, good news steph finished with fuckwit b/f and thinks hes a weirdo too! bad news.have mountain of coursework to complete.....bugger

What obscure band are you? HA! Why oh why has julian decided not to wash his hair like, ever??! *dances* tres tres sleepy. But i'm now on my hols!! Been working 2day. very sleepy and covered in scratchsfrom bloody roses. Saw the dawn parade on tues. They were pop a rooney and it was barney bastardo! fucking manics fans...... FISCHERSPOONER WAS ON TOTPS IN SLIVER PANTS!!!!!! *screams* hehe twas muchos funny. he was wasted on that crowd. me not seeing craig n e more. dont care really. me happy :) tomorrow i will get hair cut, go to work then go shopping in leeds :) dont think i'm going to the gig. busy busy day, busy me think they thought i was 18 at the casbah :) and got into the club at barfly :) 'magic monkey dust' whicle all the twats from my skool got thrown out for being underage! HA! dad has used the shredder without informing me *chuh* how dare he i'm going to go make and top and paint my nails and go lalalala while talking to miss suzy mwahmwahmwah 'you know ur a manics fan when... You are so used to all your clothes being covered in arty literary quotes that you have come to believe that "50% ACRYLIC, 50% POLYESTER, DO NOT TUMBLE DRY" is a quotation by Camus. ' HA!
THERES A BADGER ON THE TV CALLED SIMON...CUD BE JEFF BUT ITS STILL A BADGER!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Which PPG would you be?

i can talk to squirrels..there was a squashed one outside the skool gates the other day....twas aaaaallll flat..bless it

I DO NOT like you live journal...you are tres confuzzling.

Today i got up at 12.00 :) and  j'ai regarde la tele, twas le football. Woooo brazil won *yay* they have pretty coloured shirts.  i have just painted my nails bright red and they look fantabulus :D *indeedykins* mmmm yes.  i will finish my drama in a mo.....why do i  ALWAYS leave things to the last minute??

OOOOOO lauren laverne on glastonbury she is presenting it!!! oh i love her.  I saw the vines set...he kept going urrrggggghhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh and gurning A LOT! coz he is ROCK. want his babies...do im..

i keep forgetting to add my more friends to this..i will get around to it

Went shop shop shopping yesterday.  Saw steph, not mad with her n e more, love her again.  she saw shcuh boy with  a man with a pink bra on...i got alarmed coz i thought schuh boy had a pink bra on..

smudged my nail buggerbuggerbugger

I bought sum nail varnish and 2 tops from topshop and a lippy and eyeliner :D will wear said top to the d4 gig.steph going with me now. i cant moan about it. bugger. couldnt find the d4 album ANYWHERE in town...i'll getit after work tomorrow in hillsborough.
i tried on a pink glittery top in mark one sale *spot the manics fan* but didnt get it coz i'm stupid.

Then i went to see stephs mosher mateys on devenshire green. *shudders*

girl: hello y'know steph?
me:yep
girl: u like sum41?
me: no
girl: bye
then girl and group bugger off.god i have soooo many friends

there was a mini tent and two sheep on devenshire green..no one seemed to notice.. i think they thought they were hallucenating. like a mini glastonbury.
Them all medevil type blokes came with stabby stabby swords.  One ran towards me going 'uuugggghhhhh' i think he thought he was in the vines...
then walked along to rocky horror...looking at the bootiful floor when i saw sum bananananana feet. twas bailey :) he had a ickle matey and was eating chips. he went and sat down and watched vines man run around with a sword..i gave him a fanzine, made general chit chat then ran b4 he cud open it.
then i went home coz my feet hurt.  wrote a song that wasnt about a teapot strangley enough, didnt mention badgers or beards either...shit. i shall write 'the ballad of bb beard'
i am rambling,i will use this to ramble :D

i miss laalaa, but i get a big room to myself


must do drama...bugger....

*theres a worm at the bottom of my garden and his name is wiggly wooo*

can u tell i'm trying to avoid doing work yet?
